{"tid":2389742,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓女團GFriend隊長25歲Sowon疑甜攬納粹黨軍人蠟像惹爭議","createTime":"2021-02-01T06:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T13:58:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3490dcce4219508df2e660f7bccddea834930a41","tid":2389742,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HGrx3Kj9VDfOmLDwy618YudE9-k=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V4FWUIYE5FFC7NVHHKSWGXF6CQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHGrx3Kj9VDfOmLDwy618YudE9-k%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV4FWUIYE5FFC7NVHHKSWGXF6CQ.jpg&h=5bd37ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國女團GFriend出道6年，在海外亦擁有不少fans，但25歲隊長Sowon昨日在IG上載兩張靚相分享近況時，卻引起海外fans不滿。<br />\n<br />\n被質疑認同大屠殺<br />\n相中，Sowon對一個身穿軍服的蠟像又攬、又摸，兼大晒甜美笑容，顯得十分享受，但fans就發現該蠟像穿着德國納粹黨軍服，由於Sowon笑容燦爛地攬着蠟像合照，此舉被海外fans鬧爆她無知、不熟悉歷史，甚至有人批她等於認同納粹軍當年進行大屠殺的暴行。<br />\n<br />\n急刪相補鑊<br />\n對於爆出爭議，Sowon已急急刪除照片，但相片已在網上瘋傳，有不少海外fans紛紛留言要求Sowon及其所屬事務所道歉，目前事務所未有任何回應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fJJlrM5ErHZ07yEJ0TriUmv5xTI=/802x953/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BIB7EKIZQZA3XHJODYI3V4RREE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfJJlrM5ErHZ07yEJ0TriUmv5xTI%3D%2F802x953%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBIB7EKIZQZA3XHJODYI3V4RREE.jpg&h=ec65c5d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/d6MyNfSqR5RjdrFjf8kc6W6lvK4=/802x1168/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AJV6M4PDXVF4TN5IHCZURPK5H4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fres